            <h2 class="text-head">Immigrate to Canada</h2>
            <h3>Canada Immigration: What are your options?</h3>
            Despite the global coronavirus pandemic, Canada has set a target of welcoming over 400,000 new immigrants each year, between 2021-2023.
<br> Canada offers one of the world's most open and dynamic immigration systems. There are over 100 different Canadian immigration pathways for skilled workers, business people, and families. Our page helps you explore the details of the programs to give you an idea which options may be best for you.
